{
  "words": [
    {
      "w": "Every summer,",
      "s": 0.5,
      "e": 1.428,
      "seg": 0
    },
    {
      "w": "Alaska has to count its caribou.",
      "s": 1.528,
      "e": 3.519,
      "seg": 0
    },
    {
      "w": "On the North Slope,",
      "s": 3.939,
      "e": 5.043,
      "seg": 1
    },
    {
      "w": "one herd can run into the tens of thousands.",
      "s": 5.143,
      "e": 7.774,
      "seg": 1
    },
    {
      "w": "Biologists fly the tundra",
      "s": 8.194,
      "e": 9.817,
      "seg": 2
    },
    {
      "w": "and bring back thousands of aerial photos.",
      "s": 9.917,
      "e": 12.391,
      "seg": 2
    },
    {
      "w": "Then a person has to find",
      "s": 12.811,
      "e": 14.413,
      "seg": 3
    },
    {
      "w": "every animal in every frame.",
      "s": 14.513,
      "e": 16.44,
      "seg": 3
    },
    {
      "w": "A new model from Microsoft's AI for Good lab",
      "s": 16.86,
      "e": 19.859,
      "seg": 4
    },
    {
      "w": "learns each caribou from a single dot,",
      "s": 19.96,
      "e": 22.24,
      "seg": 4
    },
    {
      "w": "not a boxed outline.",
      "s": 22.339,
      "e": 23.665,
      "seg": 4
    },
    {
      "w": "Those dots are up to seven times faster",
      "s": 24.086,
      "e": 26.485,
      "seg": 5
    },
    {
      "w": "and three times cheaper to draw.",
      "s": 26.585,
      "e": 28.348,
      "seg": 5
    },
    {
      "w": "On Alaska's 2022 Central Arctic survey,",
      "s": 28.768,
      "e": 32.496,
      "seg": 6
    },
    {
      "w": "its count landed within about three percent of the herd.",
      "s": 32.596,
      "e": 35.656,
      "seg": 6
    },
    {
      "w": "But the model has a limit.",
      "s": 36.076,
      "e": 37.638,
      "seg": 7
    },
    {
      "w": "Where the animals crowd together,",
      "s": 37.738,
      "e": 39.462,
      "seg": 7
    },
    {
      "w": "its count starts to slip.",
      "s": 39.562,
      "e": 41.044,
      "seg": 7
    },
    {
      "w": "It counts what the camera sees.",
      "s": 41.464,
      "e": 43.31,
      "seg": 8
    },
    {
      "w": "It cannot fly the plane, or find the herd.",
      "s": 43.41,
      "e": 45.877,
      "seg": 8
    },
    {
      "w": "So the plane still flies, the model counts,",
      "s": 46.296,
      "e": 48.842,
      "seg": 9
    },
    {
      "w": "and the number comes home sooner.",
      "s": 48.942,
      "e": 50.62,
      "seg": 9
    }
  ],
  "speech_end": 50.62,
  "total": 60.0,
  "fps": 30
}